Package net.tfobz.vocabletrainer.gui.dialogs

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    VocableTrainer2OptionDialog
    A dialog with two options that can be used to get a binary decision (Yes/No, Accept/Decline, etc.) from the user.
    VocableTrainerColorChooser
    A GUI class representing a dialog for selecting and applying colors in the Vocable Trainer application.
    VocableTrainerInfoDialog
    A dialog displaying information to the user with formatted text and a close button.
    VocableTrainerInputDialog
    Represents an input dialog for the Vocable Trainer application.
    VocableTrainerNewSetDialog
    Dialog for creating a new vocabulary set in the Vocable Trainer application.
